mainText.detailsOne: Cardboard Citizen is an Art Blockchain project. This collection contains 6767 cute cardboards that have been inspired by Danbo (a fictional cardboard box robot character from manga series Yotsuba&! Created in 2003)
mainText.detailsTwo: We represent holders in our platform of outcome that enables profit and non-profit to achieve accountability on their social actions. This is done with our protocols in the Good 2 Earn system.
